txt.en: 'I am concerned that a number of Easterlings still occupy Lang Rhuven. Perhaps destroying their camps will cause them to flee.'
You should return to Candúr, who can be found at a small Ranger outpost hidden in the Slag-hills.
Candúr is concerned with the number of Easterlings still occupying Lang Rhuven.
Easterling tents and banners can be found in Lang Rhuven on the border of Dagorlad.\n\nYou should destroy tents and banners found in Lang Rhuven.
'I commend you on your efforts. You have shown dedication for our cause.'
Destroy groups of tents in Lang Rhuven ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
